olt Offshore Wind Farm|Anholt]] || 400 || {{DNK}} || {{coord|56|36|00|N|11|12|36|E |type:landmark_region:DK |name=Anholt Offshore Wind Farm}} || 111 \u00d7 Siemens SWT-3.6-120 || 2013 ||<ref>\"[http://www.rechargenews.com/wind/article1336397.ece VIPs cut ribbon at 400MW Anholt]\" ''Recharge News'', 4 September 2013. Accessed: 4 September 2013.</ref><ref>Jan Bjerre Lauridsen & S\u00f8ren Andersen. \"[http://www.b.dk/nationalt/dronning-oenskede-god-vind-til-kaempemoeller-i-kattegat Queen says Good Wind to giant turbines]\" ''[[Berlingske]]'', 4 September 2013. Accessed: 4 September 2013.</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.dongenergy.com/anholt/EN/News/anholt_nyheder/News/Pages/AllturbinesatAnholtoffshorewindfarmnowoperational.aspx |title=All turbines at Anholt Offshore wind farm now operational |date=20 June 2013 |publisher=[[DONG Energy]] |accessdate=27 August 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006224732/http://www.dongenergy.com/anholt/EN/News/anholt_nyheder/News/Pages/AllturbinesatAnholtoffshorewindfarmnowoperational.aspx |archivedate=6 October 2013 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/anholt-denmark-dk13.html Anholf Offshore wind farm in 4C Offshore] Retrieved 2013-08-27</ref>\n|-\n| [[BARD Offshore 1]] || 400 || {{DEU}} || {{coord|54|22|0|N|5|59|0|E |type:landmark_region:DE |name=BARD Offshore 1}} || 80 \u00d7 BARD 5.0MW || 2013 ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/bard-offshore-i-germany-de23.html|title=BARD Offshore Wind Farm|last=|first=|date=|work=4c Offshore|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=10 June 2015}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ndr.de/regional/niedersachsen/oldenburg/offshore389.html R\u00f6sler er\u00f6ffnet Offshore-Windpark Bard 1] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828045202/http://www.ndr.de/regional/niedersachsen/oldenburg/offshore389.html |date=2013-08-28 }} Retrieved 2013-08-26</ref><ref>[https://www.offshorewind.biz/2013/08/26/german-feder