08.pdf |title=Offshore Wind Farms 2008|date=2009-02-02 |publisher=EWEA |accessdate=2009-02-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scottish-southern.co.uk/SSEInternet/index.aspx?rightColHeader=30&id=15836|title=SSE plc - The UK's broadest-based energy company|work=scottish-southern.co.uk|accessdate=10 June 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Dudgeon Offshore Wind Farm|Dudgeon]] || 402 || {{GBR}} || {{coord|53|14|56|N|1|23|24|E |type:landmark_region:GB |name=Dudgeon Offshore Wind Farm}} || 67 \u00d7 Siemens 6 MW || 2017 ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://renews.biz/108711/dudgeon-hits-cfd-milestone/|title=Dudgeon hits CfD milestone|author=|date=4 October 2017|website=renews.biz|accessdate=4 April 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Veja Mate Offshore Wind Farm|Veja Mate]] || 402 || {{DEU}} || {{coord|54|19|1|N|5|52|15|E |type:landmark_region:DE |name=Veja Mate Wind Farm}} || 67 \u00d7 Siemens SWT-6.0-154 || 2017 ||<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.offshorewind.biz/2016/04/06/worlds-largest-ow-jack-up-vessel-installs-worlds-heaviest-monopile-at-veja-mate-owf/ |title=World's Largest OW Jack-Up Vessel Installs World's Heaviest Monopile at Veja Mate OWF|accessdate=6 June 2016|date=2016-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Construction complete for 402-MW Veja Mate offshore wind park|url=https://renewablesnow.com/news/construction-complete-for-402-mw-veja-mate-offshore-wind-park-570637/|website=Renewables Now|accessdate=31 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Anholt Offshore Wind Farm|Anholt]] || 400 || {{DNK}} || {{coord|56|36|00|N|11|12|36|E |type:landmark_region:DK |name=Anholt Offshore Wind Farm}} || 111 \u00d7 Siemens SWT-3.6-120 || 2013 ||<ref>\"[http://www.rechargenews.com/wind/article1336397.ece VIPs cut ribbon at 400MW Anholt]\" ''Recharge News'', 4 September 2013. Accessed: 4 September 2013.</ref><ref>Jan Bjerre Lauridsen & S\u00f8ren Andersen. \"[http://www.b.dk/nationalt/dronning-oenskede-god-vind-til-kaempemoeller-i-kattegat Queen says Good Wind to giant turbines]\" ''[[Berlingske]]'', 4 September 2013. Accessed: 4 September 2013.</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.dongenergy.com/anholt/EN/News/anholt_nyheder/News/Pages/AllturbinesatAnholtoffshorewindfarmnowoperational.aspx |title=All turbines at Anholt Offshore wind farm now operational |date=20 June 2013 |publisher=[[DONG Energy]] |accessdate=27 August 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006224732/http://www.dongenergy.com/anholt/EN/News/anholt_nyheder/News/Pages/AllturbinesatAnholtoffshorewindfarmnowoperational.aspx |archivedate=6 October 2013 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/anholt-denmark-dk13.html Anholf Offshore wind farm in 4C Offshore] Retrieved 2013-08-27</ref>\n|-\n| [[BARD Offshore 1]] || 400 || {{DEU}} || {{coord|54|22|0|N|5|59|0|E |type:landmark_region:DE |name=BARD Offshore 1}} || 80 \u00d7 BARD 5.0MW || 2013 ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/bard-offshore-i-germany-de23.html|title=BARD Offshore Wind Farm|last=|first=|date=|work=4c Offshore|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=10 June 2015}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ndr.de/regional/niedersachsen/oldenburg/offshore389.html R\u00f6sler er\u00f6ffnet Offshore-Windpark Bard 1] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828045202/http://www.ndr.de/regional/niedersachsen/oldenburg/offshore389.html |date=2013-08-28 }} Retrieved 2013-08-26</ref><ref>[https://www.offshorewind.biz/2013/08/26/german-federal-minister-inaugurates-bard-offshore-1/ German Federal Minister Inaugurates BARD Offshore 1] Retrieved 2013-08-26</ref>\n|-\n| {{interlanguage link|Global Tech I Wind Farm|lt=Global Tech I|de|Offshore-Windpark Global Tech I}} || 400 || {{DEU}} || {{coord|54|30|00|N|6|21|30|E |type:landmark_region:DE |name=Global Tech I}} || 80 \u00d7 [[Areva Wind|Areva Multibrid]] M5000 5.0MW|| 2015 ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sunwindenergy.com/offshore-wind-energy/global-tech-officially-inaugurated|title=Global Tech I officially inaugurated|work=sunwindenergy.com/|access